(area_cell_count, area_cell_count).explanation: A variable cannot cause itself as they represent the same measurement;

(area_cell_count, time).explanation: Increasing the number of cells in a chip design directly increases the computational complexity and processing time required for design tools and simulations;

(area_cell_count, area_net_area).explanation: A higher number of cells in the design necessitates more interconnect routing between cells, directly increasing the net area required for wiring;
